Magic Lore No Drop<br>
Slot:Charm<br>
Race: ALL<br>
Class: ALL<br>
<br>
Item Information:<br>
Improves as your faction with the Emerald Warriors increases<br>
<br>
Stats at warmly faction = AC 1 +5 dex +9 HP +9 SV Poison<br>
<br>
Stats at Ally faction = AC 2 +5 dex +10 HP +10 SV Poison<br>
