Found by Completing the Medallion of Service quest in Neriak on top of the warrior Guild<br>
<br>
Medallions of Service Drop in Dulak Harbour Just gotta be there a little while.<br>
<br>
Bronze, Silver, Gold, And Platinum Medallions of Service are needed.<br>
